QuestData.Title: Look to the Overlook
QuestData.Description:
$n, I have another task for you.
There have been reports of Primalist activity near the Gelikyr Post that threaten our control of Tyrhold.
Speak with Commander Thadezus and see how you can assist.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Commander Thadezus at the Gelikyr Overlook.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Commander Thadezus at the Gelikyr Overlook.
QuestData.RewardText:
<Thadezus sighs deeply.>
You are telling me that Drine sent you?
